# Build artifacts for the CCA HIP kernel — never commit (ABI binds to the image's
# torch; the .so is built in-image by Dockerfile.zaya). Mirrors the repo's
# no-prebuilt-.so rule (CONTRIBUTING "the one hard rule: ABI").
**/build/
**/*.so
**/*.egg-info/
# hipify byproducts (setup.py emits *_hip.cpp / *_hip.hip next to the source)
**/*_hip.cpp
**/*_hip.hip
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
